data.title: Souce Najib Leadership
data.meta_description: Souce Najib Leadership - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. This document provides background information on Najib Razak, the current Prime Minister of Malaysia. It discusses his leadership style and roles/expectations of a Prime Minister. Najib received his education in the UK and held roles at Bank Negara and PETRONAS before entering politics. He has served as Minister of Culture, Youth, and Sports as well as Minister of Defense. The document analyzes Najib's leadership in the context of Malaysia's history and progress under its five Prime Ministers.
